{
  "stem": "521.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were writing letters to each other every second day, and like with my parents and with my fiancee, we have communicated very well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was, actually, in those days somehow in-- in '43, somehow the Hungarian anti-Jewish laws were relaxed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It means that the Jews weren't persecuted openly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they weren't really-- they weren't really murdered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just more or less a normal life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only reason we felt [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bad because there was still discrimination between soldiers and-- and-- and forced labors-- forced laborers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, it was a very sudden-- I've mentioned before that we were digging holes, which was futile.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we were also trained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, when the regular soldier had a gun, and he was exercising with a gun, we were-- we had received a spade from the Hungarian government.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were exercising with a spade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The spade looks like a gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they wanted us to go through the routine exercise as if you would do it with a gun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, I-- I will say, in those days, the Hungarian military wasn't with forced laborers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They weren't really very, very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were treating us fairly well, especially they were treating me fairly well, because as I told you before, I never wanted to rock the boat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I behaved.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was never arguing with anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was never doing anything against the rules.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, other boys, other forced laborers, we were at that time 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had another group who was 22 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were doing our job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But certain kids, they were doing-- they went out in the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they didn't come back until late.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
